\SE[7]Nikita, I wonder if you're okay... I hope you haven't
been through anything difficult...

\SE[20]Well, that's true. \.It's not like I don't trust Vega
and the others, but... \!\SE[48]I still feel a bit uneasy,
you know...

\SE[21]No, that's too optimistic! \SE[0]But... thank you. I
feel better now.

\SE[2]By the way... everyone, aren't you a little late?
\SE[3]I wonder what is taking so long?

\SE[4]Wh-What? \.What's wrong? \!\SE[2]Hurry up and come
over here.

\SE[28]I-I apologize for the difficulty in saying this...
\!\SE[24]It seems that... my buttocks... are stuck...
\!\SE[64]I can't go any further... neither forward nor
backward...

\SE[46]Stop it...! Don't look at me like that...!! \SE[65]I
just wanted to be an example for all of you...! \SE[28]It
wasn't supposed to be like this...!!

\SE[11]...So, what are we going to do? \.There's no other
route, right? \!\SE[12]Laura is stuck and there's nothing we
can do about it.

\SE[12]What to do... There's only pulling or pushing left,
right? \SE[0]Let's try pushing a little. \SE[14].........
Hup.

\SE[14]Hey, where do you think you're touching...!?
\!\SE[27]You're the worst...!! \.I seriously can't believe
it...!!! \!\SE[24]Pervert!! \.Idiot!! \.Cheater!!

\SE[14]But, it can't be helped, right? \!\SE[12]If we don't
touch, it won't start!

\SE[14]So noisy!!! \.I don't want to hear any excuses like
that!! \!\SE[29]Idiot!! \.Idiot!! \.Idiot!!!

\SE[57]Ah... Well then, Vita. \SE[3]How about it? Do you
think it's possible?

\SE[16]Hmm... It might be a little tough. \SE[15]It's
unbelievable how perfectly it fits. \SE[2]We'll have to
break through the wall or tear Laura apart...

\SE[21]W-Well, that's really not good... \!\SE[0]I guess
there's no other choice. \.Lunaroa.\.Let's go together, just
the two of us.

\SE[46]Don't look at me! \SE[42]Don't look at me like
this...!!
\SE[17]Laura is done for! Leave this to us and go ahead...!

\SE\SE[2]Is there no good way to consult with the Guild?
\.They might have connections with construction workers or
something. \!\SE[2]But Laura's private parts will be
exposed....
\SE[3]Hmm.... Things aren't going as planned, huh....
\SE[46] Please... leave me alone for a little while...
